text: KHF Shqiponja is a women's handball club from Gjakova in western Kosovo. KHF Shqiponja competes in the SuperLiga e femrave e Kosoves and the Kosovo Handball Women's Cup. ==European record == {| class="wikitable" ! Season ! Competition ! Round ! Club ! 1st leg ! 2nd leg !
